@node "Buglist" "Buglist"

@{MS "Buglist"}

Well it isnÇt possible to use disks while TrackDisplayClock is running, but this is logical infact
that we use the diskdrive position to view the time. If you want to use disks, then use the hotkey,
Exchange or other programs to disable TrackdiskClock for this periode.

@endnode
